<body bgcolor=3D"#27282C" lang=3DEN-AU style=3D'tab-interval:36.0pt'>

<div class=3DWordSection1>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>Bacon Mod for Distant Worlds Universe<o:p></o:p>=
</span></b></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:8.0pt'>By Roger Bacon<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:8.0pt'>Help file for mod vers=
ion 1.79<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>Usage<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Many of the settings of this mod can be set by the pla=
yer in
the BaconSettings.txt file. Feel free to change and adjust as you see fit.<=
/p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Note: All references to settings refer to BaconSetting=
s.txt
file.</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>Changes<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Gravity Wells=
</b>:
Stars generate a gravity well preventing ships from initiating a <span
class=3DSpellE>hyperjump</span> if <span class=3DSpellE>useStarGravityWells=
</span>=3Dtrue.</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Crew experien=
ce
levels</b>: Crew gain experience when inflicting damage (and can lose it if
they take too much damage). View with Ctrl-s. Each level above
&#8220;Green&#8221; gives a random bonus to the ship.</p>

